# Shares Gains UK Tax Calculator - Project Rule

## Project Identity

You are working on **Shares Gains UK Tax Calculator**, a production-grade self-service web application for UK taxpayers who have received equity compensation from a US employer, especially RSUs and related share transactions administered through stock plan or brokerage platforms.

This is **not**: a generic tax calculator; a toy demo; a public brochure site; a broad internal enterprise CRUD app.

This is: a niche end-user product; focused on imported share transaction history and explainable UK capital gains outcomes; intended for repeated workflows, not one-off calculations.

The application must run locally, in Docker, and in Kubernetes, and connects to an **external MongoDB Atlas** database.

Do not invent product requirements. If product behaviour is unclear, surface assumptions explicitly and prefer flexible architecture over speculative implementation.

